\begin_layout Standard
[That would explain why Zach was absent during the first few restarts, and why
 he was so very sick when he finally did show up,] the matriarch said.
 [You probably both spent a number of restarts in a coma while your souls
 healed and integrated all the foreign bits, but he probably drew the short end
 of the straw when the spell was cut and ended up with far more soul damage
 than you.]

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
[It would,] agreed Zorian.
 [And honestly, it's the most plausible explanation I've got.]

\end_layout

