 I am not integral to this time loop in any way, and can be disposed of at
 whim.
 If I talk to Zach, and he's being watched, or if Zach is unable to keep his
 mouth shut in front of the wrong people, I could end up being… deleted.]

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
[Well…] the matriarch said.
 [You're certainly one paranoid human.
 Then again, that might be the only reason why you're still in possession of
 your entire memory, so maybe I shouldn't talk.
 You do realize you're going to have to talk to Zach at some point, right?]

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
[Hopefully not before I identify the third time traveler,] Zorian said.

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
[Then we should make it a priority to track him down,] the matriarch said.

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
[How?] Zorian asked.
 [I don't even know where to start.
 It could be anyone.]

